Album: BlondeArtiste:Frank OceanGenre: Alternative R&amp;BRelease: August 20Frank Ocean stunned the world by releasing two albums in just 48 hours: Endless the visual album and strategic build up to Blonde . Essentials tracks include Pink + White, Skyline To, Self Control, White Ferrari and Godspeed. Key collaborators include Kanye West, Andre 3000, Beatles, James Blake, Kendrick Lamar, Pharell Williams and Beyonce. Frank Ocean brilliantly narrates his life experiences and continues to prove to the world that he is a master at his art.Star Rating: 4 out of 5